{
  "id": "adv_card_kkr_01_02",
  "title": "赤崎こころ 2話 ポージングの特訓",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（意外にも、こころ単独で雑誌の依頼が舞い込んだな）\n（彼女にとってこれは大きなチャンスだ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Kokoro has received an unexpected offer for a solo magazine shoot.)\n(This is a big chance for her.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "どうして、ポージングの特訓なのに\n二人だけなんですか～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s supposed to be posing practice for me!\nWhy is it just the two of us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.733333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "悩殺ポーズをこころに授けてくれる\n敏腕コーチはどこですか～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Where’s the super posing coach\nwho’s going to teach me the ultimate pose?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "……というか「意外にも」って\nみんなのアイドル、こころちゃんに失礼です～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That “unexpected” part was quite rude too.\nI’m everyone’s idol! Nothing is unexpected!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "こころ、俺の心を的確に読むのはやめてくれないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro‚ can you please stop reading my mind like that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "私は常に周囲の顔色を読んで、有利な立場で発言する\nようにしてますから、自然に読めちゃうんです～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m always absorbing all the information around me.\nI just naturally pick this stuff out of the air.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "そして困った時には、よく愛ちゃんに押し付け――\n助けてもらってるんです～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And when I get into trouble‚ I put it all on Ai-chan.\nShe’s always willing to help me out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "こころ、愛が可哀想だからほどほどにな\nまあみんな、こころの腹黒キャラはもう知ってるけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t take advantage of her too much‚ okay?\nI guess everyone knows you as the sinister schemer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "こころは、腹黒くなんかないです\n人として当然の立ち居振舞いだと思うんですよね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not sinister or a schemer!\nI’m just doing what comes naturally.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい、分かったから\nポージングの練習をしようか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure‚ sure. I get it.\nLet’s do some posing‚ shall we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、コーチがいませんけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But there’s no coach.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "今日連絡してすぐに捕まる人なんて、いないよ\nとりあえずモデルさんの写真を参考に二人で練習しよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t get someone at such short notice.\nLet’s look at some photos and try this ourselves‚ shall we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "はあ～満足な練習環境もないなんて\nこんなので大丈夫なんでしょうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? You can’t even provide a proper learning environment?\nIs this really going to work out?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "もし、私がグラビアでヘマをしたら\nリズノワのみんなにも迷惑をかけてしまいます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I screw this work up‚\nit’s going to make trouble for LizNoir too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……なんだかんだ言って、みんなが大切なんだな\nもっとその気持ちを素直に出せばいいのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re always joking around‚ but you’re concerned about them too.\nYou should let those feelings out a little more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "……な～んて、ちょっと真面目な所を見せれば\nみんなコロッと態度が変わるんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hah‚ see? I just get serious for a moment\nand it throws you right off your game. Works every time!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……やっぱり、こころはこころだな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I walked into that one. Kokoro gotta Kororo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.46666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "すみませ～ん。私は愛ちゃんと違って\n簡単に男性に懐いたりはしないんです～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I’m sorry! Unlike Ai-chan‚\nI don’t bat my eyelids at every man who comes along.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "愛ちゃんと莉央さんと葵さんにしか\n心を開きませんので～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai-chan‚ Rio-san‚ and Aoi-san\nare the only ones I’m truly open with!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.56666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そうか。必要以上に仲良くなる必要はないけど\n仕事仲間としては、俺や他の子達も信頼してほしいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Well‚ we don’t have to become best buddies‚\nbut I hope you’ll trust me‚ and the other girls‚ as your colleagues.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ{user}さん\nこころの好感度を頑張って上げて下さいね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case‚ {user}-san‚\nyou’d better work on raising your approval rating with me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（詳しいことは分からないけど）\n（何か事情があるのかもしれないな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I don’t know the details‚)\n(but there has to be something behind her attitude.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.43333333333337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（こころにも星見プロを好きになってもらいたい）\n（そのためにも今回の仕事、俺も気合いを入れないとな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I want her to like it here at Hoshimi Productions.)\n(I need to give this work some serious attention myself.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "こ、こんな感じですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-something like this? What do you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "背筋を伸ばして立つのはいいけど\nつま先立ちはしないで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s good to stand straight‚\nbut no need to stand on tip-toes like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "だって、ちょっとでも、背が高く見られたいです\n足も長く見えた方が――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to look as tall as possible.\nI want my legs to look longer as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.26666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "気持ちは分かるけど、かえって背が低い印象になるから\nほら、動画を見て、まずは軸足を決めるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand the instinct‚ but it just makes you look smaller.\nWatch this video. Decide the axis for your leg first.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "ふむふむ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmmm‚ okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "足をクロスして、膝より上を体より前に出す\nそれで長く見える",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Cross your legs‚ then put everything above the knee in front of your body.\nThat makes your legs look longer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.26666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
